	   <tr><td colspan=2>1h weaps are almost always faster than comperable 2h weaps.&nbsp;&nbsp;With the primary hand damage bonus, the faster the weapon, the more often this extra damage lands.  This is why lammys outdamage centi LS, even though the cLS has a better dam/dly ratio.  You also benefit from the ability to bash with a shield, let alone the stats, which you mentioned yourself.  Many 1h weaps have ratios similar to equivilant 2h weapons, and benefit from the increased speed.  I would use a noct blade, for instance, over an oggok cleaver.  The oggok cleaver may have a better ratio but is more than twice as slow, meaning it will have much less effect from the damage bonus, let alone the shield can be very usefull.  <br>&nbsp;<br>Ok, I'll shut up now.<br><br>Baron Slein Jinn &lt;Dawn of Redemption&gt;<br>Grave Lord on everyone's least favorite server, E'ci<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325772" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325772</a></td></tr>
